---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../content/site.ts';

const title = `Terms of Service | ${siteConfig.name}`;
const description = 'Terms of Service for Solvin IT — the rules that govern use of this website and our services.';
const effectiveDate = 'May 19, 2026';
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description} noIndex={false}>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">

      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="heading-1 text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Effective date: {effectiveDate}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose-legal">

        <p>
          Please read these Terms of Service ("Terms") carefully before using the website at <a href={siteConfig.url}>{siteConfig.url}</a> (the "Site") or any services or software products offered by <strong>Solvin IT</strong>, operated by Jose Fernando Gonzales ("we," "us," or "our"). By accessing or using the Site you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, do not use the Site.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Services</h2>
        <p>
          Solvin IT provides the following, which are collectively referred to as the "Services":
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Portfolio website</strong> — informational content about our work, projects, and professional background.</li>
          <li><strong>AI chatbot (Fred the AI Butler)</strong> — an interactive assistant that answers questions about Jose Fernando Gonzales's professional experience and projects.</li>
          <li><strong>Consulting and engineering services</strong> — AI/ML engineering, technical solutions consulting, and software development engagements contracted separately by written or email agreement.</li>
          <li><strong>Open-source software</strong> — code repositories published under their respective open-source licences.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Eligibility</h2>
        <p>
          You must be at least 13 years old to use the Site. By using the Site you represent that you meet this requirement. If you are using the Site on behalf of an organisation, you represent that you have authority to bind that organisation to these Terms.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use the Site or Services for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable law or regulation.</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorised access to any part of the Site, its servers, or any connected systems.</li>
          <li>Transmit any malicious code, spam, or unsolicited bulk communications through any feature of the Site (including the contact form or chatbot).</li>
          <li>Scrape, crawl, or systematically download content from the Site in a manner that places an unreasonable load on our infrastructure.</li>
          <li>Misrepresent your identity or affiliation when contacting us.</li>
          <li>Use the AI chatbot to submit sensitive personal information (financial data, government ID numbers, health information, passwords, etc.).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All original content on the Site — including text, graphics, design, and code (except where a separate open-source licence applies) — is the property of Jose Fernando Gonzales and is protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from this content without prior written permission.
        </p>
        <p>
          Open-source repositories linked from the Site are governed by their own licences (typically MIT). Nothing in these Terms restricts rights granted by those licences.
        </p>
        <p>
          Any feedback, suggestions, or ideas you voluntarily provide to us may be used without restriction and without compensation to you.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Third-Party Links and Content</h2>
        <p>
          The Site may contain links to third-party websites (GitHub, LinkedIn, live project demos, etc.). We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of those sites. A link does not constitute an endorsement.
        </p>

        <h2>6. AI Chatbot — Limitations and Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          The Fred AI Butler is designed to provide information about our professional portfolio. Its responses are generated by a language model and may be incomplete, inaccurate, or outdated. You should not rely on chatbot output as professional, legal, financial, or technical advice. We make no warranty that responses are error-free.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Consulting and Contracted Services</h2>
        <p>
          Specific consulting or development engagements are governed by a separate written agreement (Statement of Work, contract, or email exchange confirming scope and terms). In the event of a conflict between these Terms and a separate agreement, the separate agreement controls for that engagement.
        </p>
        <p>
          Unless otherwise stated in a separate agreement:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Deliverables are provided "as is" upon delivery.</li>
          <li>Payment terms, milestones, and revision rounds are defined per engagement.</li>
          <li>We retain ownership of any general-purpose tools, methodologies, and know-how developed during an engagement; you receive a licence to use the specific deliverables.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>
          THE SITE AND SERVICES ARE PROVIDED <strong>"AS IS"</strong> AND <strong>"AS AVAILABLE"</strong> WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, AND NON-INFRINGEMENT. WE DO NOT WARRANT THAT THE SITE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED, ERROR-FREE, OR FREE OF VIRUSES OR OTHER HARMFUL COMPONENTS.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY APPLICABLE LAW, SOLVIN IT AND JOSE FERNANDO GONZALES SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF PROFITS OR REVENUES, ARISING OUT OF OR RELATED TO YOUR USE OF THE SITE OR SERVICES, EVEN IF ADVISED OF THE POSSIBILITY OF SUCH DAMAGES.
        </p>
        <p>
          OUR TOTAL LIABILITY TO YOU FOR ANY CLAIM ARISING FROM OR RELATED TO THESE TERMS OR THE SERVICES SHALL NOT EXCEED THE GREATER OF (A) THE AMOUNT YOU PAID US IN THE 12 MONTHS PRECEDING THE CLAIM OR (B) ONE HUNDRED US DOLLARS (USD 100).
        </p>

        <h2>10. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>
          You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Solvin IT and Jose Fernando Gonzales from any claims, damages, losses, and expenses (including reasonable legal fees) arising from your use of the Site or Services in violation of these Terms or any applicable law.
        </p>

        <h2>11. Governing Law and Dispute Resolution</h2>
        <p>
          These Terms are governed by the laws of the <strong>Republic of the Philippines</strong>, without regard to conflict-of-law principles. Any dispute arising from these Terms shall first be attempted to be resolved through good-faith negotiation. If unresolved within 30 days, disputes shall be submitted to the appropriate courts located in <strong>Makati City, Metro Manila, Philippines</strong>.
        </p>

        <h2>12. Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. When we do, we will update the "Effective date" at the top of this page. Your continued use of the Site after the update constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms. If the changes are material, we will make reasonable efforts to provide notice (e.g., a notice on the Site).
        </p>

        <h2>13. Severability</h2>
        <p>
          If any provision of these Terms is found to be unenforceable, that provision will be limited or eliminated to the minimum extent necessary, and the remaining Terms will remain in full force and effect.
        </p>

        <h2>14. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these Terms may be directed to:<br />
          <strong>Jose Fernando Gonzales — Solvin IT</strong><br />
          Makati City, Philippines<br />
          <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.author.email}`}>{siteConfig.author.email}</a>
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .prose-legal {
    @apply text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-6;
  }
  .prose-legal h2 {
    @apply text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-10 mb-3;
  }
  .prose-legal h3 {
    @apply text-base font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mt-6 mb-2;
  }
  .prose-legal p {
    @apply text-base;
  }
  .prose-legal ul {
    @apply list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2 text-base;
  }
  .prose-legal a {
    @apply text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-primary-800 dark:hover:text-primary-300 transition-colors;
  }
  .prose-legal strong {
    @apply font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white;
  }
</style>
